---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Pavel Kleisner – Backend Developer & Micro-SaaS Builder">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mb-36 motion-safe:animate-[fadeUp_600ms_ease-out_1]">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-8">
            Pavel <span class="text-teal-500">Kleisner</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-2xl text-slate-400 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mb-6">
            Backend-heavy full-stack developer and tech lead focused on
            system architecture, long-term maintainability and building
            meaningful <span class="text-slate-200">micro-SaaS products</span>.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mb-12">
            I like clean systems, calm delivery, and products that solve a narrow problem really well.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="/projects"
               class="bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-medium transition">
                View projects
            </a>
            <a href="/contact"
               class="border border-slate-700 hover:border-teal-500 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-medium transition">
                Contact
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INTRO / POSITIONING -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mb-36 space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold">What I do</h2>

        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            I design and build backend systems that are meant to last.
            Systems that are understandable, maintainable and resilient
            even years after the initial implementation.
        </p>

        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            My primary focus is backend development, but my full-stack
            background allows me to understand products as a whole —
            from database design and APIs to frontend needs and user experience.
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- HIGHLIGHTS -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mb-36">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-10">Selected highlights</h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Backend & architecture</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Clear responsibilities, predictable data flows, and systems that age well.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Pragmatic delivery</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Choosing the simplest viable approach, with an eye on long-term costs.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Micro-SaaS mindset</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Small, focused products with real users and ownership end-to-end.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- EXPERIENCE -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mb-36">
        <div class="flex items-end justify-between gap-6 mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold">Experience</h2>
            <div class="flex gap-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">
                <span class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">9+ years</span>
                <span class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Team lead since 2023</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-10">
            <div class="border-l border-slate-800 pl-6">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Senior Backend-heavy Full-stack Engineer / Team Lead</h3>
                    <span class="text-slate-500">DataLite, s.r.o.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">January 2017 – Present · Prague, Czech Republic</div>
                <ul class="text-slate-300 space-y-2">
                    <li>Long-term ownership of complex production systems focused on stability and maintainability.</li>
                    <li>Backend architecture, database design, integrations, and technical decisions for core systems.</li>
                    <li>Since 2023: leading the engineering team, mentoring developers, and delivery accountability.</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4 text-xs text-slate-400">
                    <span class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Java</span>
                    <span class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Kotlin</span>
                    <span class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Spring</span>
                    <span class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Kafka</span>
                    <span class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Kubernetes</span>
                    <span class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Oracle</span>
                    <span class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">PostgreSQL</span>
                    <span class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Angular</span>
                    <span class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">CI/CD</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="border-l border-slate-800 pl-6">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Sales</h3>
                    <span class="text-slate-500">Elektro Juránek</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">August 2014 – December 2016</div>
            </div>

            <div class="border-l border-slate-800 pl-6">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Tester</h3>
                    <span class="text-slate-500">GMC Software</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">November 2013 – January 2014 · Hradec Králové, Czech Republic</div>
                <p class="text-slate-300">Use-case creation and implementation, Jenkins server operations.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- EDUCATION + CERTS -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mb-36 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
        <div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 space-y-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Education</h2>
            <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">Czech Technical University in Prague</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">BSc · Software Technologies & Management · 2009 – 2013</div>
                <p class="text-slate-300 mt-2">
                    Studied Web & Multimedia. Bachelor thesis: vector graphics editor with speech and non-speech input.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">University of Pardubice</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Microprocessor Technology · 2008 – 2009</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 space-y-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Licenses & certifications</h2>
            <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">Version control system GIT</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">CZ.NIC · June 2018</div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">Maven</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Ing. Jiří Pinkas · November 2013</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- COMMUNITY -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mb-36">
        <div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Community</h2>
            <div class="text-slate-300">
                Organizer · Charity in Červený Kostelec (since December 2015)
            </div>
            <div class="text-slate-300 mt-2">
                Film screenings in Červený Kostelec (December 2015 – 2020)
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- HOW I WORK -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mb-36 space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold">How I work</h2>
        <ul class="text-slate-300 space-y-3">
            <li>Simple boundaries and explicit naming to reduce future cognitive load.</li>
            <li>Close alignment with product goals and real-world constraints.</li>
            <li>Strong preference for boring, proven tech when it keeps systems stable.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- NOW -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mb-36 space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Now (February 2026)</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            Building and iterating on small SaaS tools, while helping teams keep their backend systems calm and maintainable.
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-600 to-teal-700 rounded-3xl p-16 max-w-6xl">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">
            Interested in working together?
        </h2>

        <p class="text-teal-100 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-3xl">
            If you’re looking for a senior backend developer,
            tech lead or technical partner for your product,
            feel free to reach out. Email works best.
        </p>

        <a href="/contact"
           class="bg-white text-teal-700 px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
            Contact me
        </a>
    </section>

</Layout>
